def calculate_remainder_of_sum_of_T_primes(S: str, T: str) -> int:
    mod = 1000000008
    n = len(T)
    s = list(map(int, S))
    t = [int(char) if char.isdecimal() else char for char in T]
    dp = [[[0] * 2 for _ in range(2)] for _ in range(n + 1)]
    dp[0][0] = [1, 0]
    p = [pow(10, i, mod) for i in range(n)]
    for i in range(n):
        ni = i + 1
        for j in range(2):
            if t[i] == '?':
                x = 9 if j else s[i]
                for d in range(x + 1):
                    nj = j | (d < s[i])
                    dp[ni][nj][0] += dp[i][j][0]
                    dp[ni][nj][1] += dp[i][j][0] * d + 10 * dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][0] %= mod
                    dp[ni][nj][1] %= mod
            else:
                d = t[i]
                nj = j | (d < s[i])
                if d <= s[i]:
                    dp[ni][nj][0] += dp[i][j][0]
                    dp[ni][nj][1] += dp[i][j][0] * d + 10 * dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][0] %= mod
                    dp[ni][nj][1] %= mod
                elif nj:
                    dp[ni][nj][0] += dp[i][j][0]
                    dp[ni][nj][1] += dp[i][j][0] * d + 10 * dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][0] %= mod
                    dp[ni][nj][1] %= mod
    result = (dp[-1][0][1] + dp[-1][1][1]) % mod
    return result

    n = len(T)
    s = list(map(int, S))
    t = [int(char) if char.isdecimal() else char for char in T]
    dp = [[[0] * 2 for _ in range(2)] for _ in range(n + 1)]
    dp[0][0] = [1, 0]
    p = [pow(10, i, mod) for i in range(n)]
    for i in range(n):
        ni = i + 1
        for j in range(2):
            if t[i] == '?':
                x = 9 if j else s[i]
                for d in range(x + 1):
                    nj = j | (d < s[i])
                    dp[ni][nj][0] += dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][1] += dp[i][j][0] * d + 10 * dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][0] %= mod
                    dp[ni][nj][1] %= mod
            else:
                d = t[i]
                nj = j | (d < s[i])
                if d <= s[i]:
                    dp[ni][nj][0] += dp[i][j][0]
                    dp[ni][nj][1] += dp[i][j][0] * d + 10 * dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][0] %= mod
                    dp[ni][nj][1] %= mod
                elif nj:
                    dp[ni][nj][0] += dp[i][j][0]
                    dp[ni][nj][1] += dp[i][j][0] * d + 10 * dp[i][j][1]
                    dp[ni][nj][0] %= mod
                    dp[ni][nj][1] %= mod
    result = (dp[-1][0][1] + dp[-1][1][1]) % mod
    return result
